We made it to Forbes 🥹✨ Alhumdulillah 

#4 in the beauty category & #43 from the top 100 digital stars list ⭐️
These past 9 years have been magical yet challenging with multiple days of self sabotaging and self doubt. Har dusre din sochti hu “ am i good enough or doing enough” bass yeh pata tha ki rukna nahi hai. 
Showing up counts & this is an example of it 🙌

No part of me would have been where i am if @mehveshkkhan wasn’t by my side~ My sister, manager, editor, creative director & lifeline 

& @fokuscreations who’s my videographer & family. Stuck through thick and thin
& most importantly, YOU GUYS #TEfam 🎀 Y’all have changed my life & this one’s for you

Visions that became my reality in 2024 🥹 Alhumdulillah ✨
-
1) wanted to experience the hot air balloon ride & finally did it in cappadocia
2) desperately wanted to see and feel snow could do that in kashmir
3) Over 3 years of this one dream: to be featured in Forbes magazine & it actually came true as they thought i was one of the top 100 digital stars of 2024
4) I love all things nature & wished to have a picnic by the pond & it happened on my 26th birthday 
5) Huge dream of attending Paris Fashion Week came true in Jan’24
6) My inner child was finally happy after vising disneyland in paris
7) I really wanted to lose fat & become healthier & i lost 5 kgs in the just 8 weeks
8) Wanted to try aerial yoga & it was so thrilling to actually do it this year
9) I posted this picture of a woman inside a mosque on my vision board, who knew? I could actually get to pray in one for the first time in turkey
10) Wanted to actually catch flights & not feelings & did manage to do it quite some in 2024
11) A meet & greet bigger & better in 2024? check ✅

What are you taking in 2025? 🤔✨

One skin habit that my future skin will thank me for definitely has to be incorporating retinol in my routine. This ingredient is not only amazing to slow down ageing, fine lines and wrinkles but also against dark spots improving skin texture and reduces acne. 

While retinol serums can also be drying, the @olayindia retinol 24 max is just perfect as it’s infused with hydrating ingredients to avoid the same unlike others in the market. 

Start with alternate night first and gradually increase to every night to achieve plumper, healthier & glowy skin.
